    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents, along with some faded paint in areas. The interior shows moderate wear including worn upholstery and some damaged trim pieces. Mechanically the car runs, but it will likely require some attention and repairs in the near term.",
